lobin-inducing agents.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/189196/', '', 'Hydroxocobalamin, Fomepizole, Ipecac, Dexrazoxane, Oxygen, Lanthanum carbonate, Difelikefalin, Cobicistat, Deferoxamine, Levoleucovorin, Promethazine, More', '', 1767369485);
